video_title: Are YOU losing your life to your Job!?
transcript:
if you died today your job would replace
you within the next couple weeks and
be fine because a job has to do that
they have to fill the position obviously
but the people who love you your family
your friends will miss you forever don't
be so caught up in a job that can
replace you immediately that you forget
to spend time with the people who really
truly matter
